																		Because if I don&#039;t write about Vincent Anderson...
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252520" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1506376250 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">25 Sep 2017 21:50</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3601425">
									

<p>Who will?</p>
<p>Had this idea came to me during a walk, and so I wrote it up. The fact that Anderson had a family that was completely abandoned has only been examined breifly in the tale <a href="/no-good-deed">No Good Deed</a> and so I felt that giving a closer look into that might be an interesting premise for a tale.</p>
<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1422059&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="tretter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1422059)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;">tretter</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-balthazaar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1468535); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1468535&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="Dr Balthazaar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1468535)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-balthazaar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1468535); return false;">Dr Balthazaar</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span> for their critique.</p>
<p>Extra special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1506376250" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span> for use of Researcher Labelle and going over her dialogue.</p>
<p>Enjoy the tale.</p>
<p><em>JC</em></p>

